      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and well-maintained ride? This car is in good condition and ready for its next owner! It runs smoothly, looks great, and has been well-cared for, making it a fantastic choice for anyone needing a dependable daily driver with plenty of life left. Come take a look and see why this is the solid, honest value you've been searching for!",
