    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained since day one. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original deep luster without a single scratch, chip, or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with high-quality materials that still look and feel brand new. Mechanically, it is perfect, with all services up to date and documented, ensuring a driving experience that is indistinguishable from a new car. This is a rare find for a collector or any buyer who demands the highest standard of excellence.",
